GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shipping

### Get Shipments for Specific Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shipping?customerEmail=customer@example.com

### Calculate Shipping Cost
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/shipping/calculate-cost?provider=FedEx&speed=Express&weight=5

